Recommends:
 vibeos-vibbey
Description: Claude Code baked-in setup for VibeOS
 Ships the first-run wizard /usr/bin/vibeos-claude-setup that walks a fresh
 user through Claude Code activation: paste an Anthropic API key (or skip),
 key is stored in the KDE Wallet / GNOME Keyring via libsecret, and a
 ~/workspace directory is scaffolded with a permissive .claude/settings.json
 suited to a dev workstation.
 .
 A login shell hook at /etc/profile.d/vibeos-claude.sh lifts the key out of
 the keyring into ANTHROPIC_API_KEY so the unmodified upstream `claude`
 binary works from any terminal without per-session setup.
 .
 Installs the "Start Coding with Claude" desktop launcher which opens
 Konsole inside ~/workspace and invokes `claude`. Ships the Claude Code
 quickstart under /usr/share/vibeos/claude-code-docs/ so Vibbey can answer
 follow-up questions without internet.
 .
 The Claude Code CLI itself (@anthropic-ai/claude-code) is installed
 globally via npm from mkosi.postinst.chroot at ISO build time, so this
 .deb does NOT pull it in at apt time.
